overview: This compilation dvd includes 10 aquatic adventures! Episodes included : The Fry Cook Games, Bubblestand, Squid's Day Off, Spongebob Meets the Stranger, Pranks a Lot, Artist Unknown, Grandma's Kisses, Krusty Love, Krab Borg, and The Smoking Peanut.
title: Spongebob Squarepant Seascape Capers
